{"tid":1229743,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"7) 連衛兵式追擊黑警 / 反對聲音","createTime":"2019-06-16T04:24:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T06:18:42.000Z","uid":183108,"like":9,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3127abf9e831673f7413334f585fb3da6131728d","tid":1229743,"uid":183108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T04:24:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">大家千萬唔好咁做</span>，拎支持既人出黎表揚已經好足夠。唔好再分裂。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">7) 連衛兵式追擊黑警 / 反對聲音<br />\n小心阿，物極必反，要適可而止。一個唔小心，就會被人連消帶打。<br />\n一方面幫對面增加仇恨，補血，另一方面仲跌埋自己個光環<br />\n呢個行為「極危險」，我明白大家好嬲，好想報復又苦無方法，呢幾日實在太多啦<br />\n唔好太過依賴呢樣方式鼓勵士氣啦</span>"},{"pid":"3230dea3ce42f6797703bb9255cccc27764ab5e3","tid":1229743,"uid":183108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T04:25:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"25e821f5d9ab712af544b13ba522e63f3f0f4d42","tid":1229743,"uid":183108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T04:25:55.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"96880f8000e60c58630087e9bd74779b2646e0bc","tid":1229743,"uid":164050,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T04:27:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fc34fb5ed8a59e5ceb3fe23d5d11b2052df76daf","tid":1229743,"uid":183108,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"96880f8000e60c58630087e9bd74779b2646e0bc","tid":1229743,"uid":164050,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T04:27:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T04:28:51.000Z","msg":"負評我都會繼續推，多謝"},{"pid":"769eaf8220ef7d11012df18885f906985d11405c","tid":1229743,"uid":183108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T04:34:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a5ac9d93d826fd02d8f439e17d3306989c98fa49","tid":1229743,"uid":183108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T04:35:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"57fa95cebb84fc0f20abaaaa17c97e315b811570","tid":1229743,"uid":183108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"